Optimum Coal Says Full-Year Production Increased 21% to 17.1 Million Tons

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-28T13:55:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/optimum-coal-says-full-year-production-increased-21-to-17-1-million-tons.html
Optimum Coal Holdings (OPT)  Ltd. said it
produced 17.1 million metric tons of run-of-mine coal during the
2011 financial year, 21 percent more than a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  